Package: pgscatalogcolors
Title: Color Palettes for PGS Catalog Ancestry Groups
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Brooke N.", "Wolford", , "brookenicholewolford@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides color palettes based on the PGS Catalog ancestry
    classification system. Maps ancestry acronyms to their official colors,
    enabling consistent and reproducible visualizations of genetic ancestry
    data. Includes ggplot2 scale functions for easy integration.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    grDevices
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    scales
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/bnwolford/pgscatalogcolors, https://www.pgscatalog.org/docs/ancestry/
BugReports: https://github.com/bnwolford/pgscatalogcolors/issues
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
